{"tid":2008211,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[擔心警察] 夏天好熱","createTime":"2020-05-09T01:08:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-09T16:41:13.000Z","uid":49784,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f4adbb19aed9ab7d0006d008e7fa3971182b3c64","tid":2008211,"uid":49784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T01:08:23.000Z","msg":"夏天咁，要全套裝備著上身，又要四圍走<br />\n<br />\n如果中午要出動點算呀，好易中暑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n宜家上面d 高層白衫又睇得咁緊，打人又比人清算<br />\n坐番10碌8碌就一世，入去比犯玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n日日都有警察比警察拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你想做拉人果個定比人拉果個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n多多少少梗有d 野做過，唔想人知<br />\n一陣比隔離果個篤出黎點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但唔篤人的話自己就比人篤，好矛盾<br />\n警隊內部批鬥已經開始，點自保？<br />\n先篤人為強？<br />\n<br />\n唔篤人就會比人篤<br />\n<br />\n有d 野不嬲都有發生<br />\n點解今日開始會唔同哂？<br />\n<br />\n點解，唔通真係要入赤柱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nd 仔女點算？<br />\n<br />\n篤定唔篤，自己諗？<br />\n鬥快已開始<br />\n<br />\n一慢左就一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14206448a8049cd156e3767555dc467b45618b95","tid":2008211,"uid":49784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T01:09:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200508/s00001/1588949826746/休班警販毒案再拘一督察一警員-涉公職失當\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200508%2Fs00001%2F1588949826746%2F%E4%BC%91%E7%8F%AD%E8%AD%A6%E8%B2%A9%E6%AF%92%E6%A1%88%E5%86%8D%E6%8B%98%E4%B8%80%E7%9D%A3%E5%AF%9F%E4%B8%80%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1-%E6%B6%89%E5%85%AC%E8%81%B7%E5%A4%B1%E7%95%B6&d=i%2FQ10njZfEvfzeNkfPb7d4T2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=66239408\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200508%2Fs00001%2F1588949826746%2F%E4%BC%91%E7%8F%AD%E8%AD%A6%E8%B2%A9%E6%AF%92%E6%A1%88%E5%86%8D%E6%8B%98%E4%B8%80%E7%9D%A3%E5%AF%9F%E4%B8%80%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1-%E6%B6%89%E5%85%AC%E8%81%B7%E5%A4%B1%E7%95%B6&h=4d2f5d7b\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200508/s00001/1588949826746/休班警販毒案再拘一督察一警員-涉公職失當</a>"},{"pid":"f3a31e599c84cc2e577be93e70ba1fa77b75aef8","tid":2008211,"uid":49784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T01:11:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200508/mobile/bkn-20200508171642348-0508_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200508%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20200508171642348-0508_00822_001.html&d=i%2FQ10njZfEvfzeNkfPb7d4T2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=fff367d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200508/mobile/bkn-20200508171642348-0508_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"14a644b3a352966f3da0b4fac21ec2be018e23e4","tid":2008211,"uid":49784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T01:11:50.000Z","msg":"通州街拘藏毒露宿者　9名警員涉妨礙司法公正被捕"},{"pid":"746ef7dfe33a640554e6be576b67b3a419649364","tid":2008211,"uid":104804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T01:23:17.000Z","msg":"我地去黃店食好西<br />\n黑警就罰企<br />\n大家小心啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"829d4ce95f047514a3b3a274262b1fa0b9f4524e","tid":2008211,"uid":49784,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T01:33:11.000Z","msg":"果d 攪緊移民嘅警察先係最高危<br />\n<br />\n因為佢地收收埋埋警隊嘅罪證，<br />\n去左外國就唔洗擔心出糧問題，都唔撈咯<br />\n<br />\n一走左佬就可以隨時爆大鑊"},{"pid":"0191b316c23c278af385971f8c46e3d64c340faa","tid":2008211,"uid":267410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T01:35:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57effb13526025e878a67c7551f1639ea238c952","tid":2008211,"uid":49784,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T01:35:20.000Z","msg":"要攪得移民<br />\n即係唔信任你地香港政府同大家嘅做事手法啦<br />\n<br />\n未唔撈梗係同大家fd 底拍膊頭，兄弟班<br />\n又話咩去左外國叫埋大家去玩"},{"pid":"a33667e5c7df7d2d01fb83288ac90282927048be","tid":2008211,"uid":214502,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T01:39:26.000Z","msg":"呢排啲狗好笑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想入商場涼冷氣就拉閘"},{"pid":"a944397bef9aa5b03a19d12073f2560802adff15","tid":2008211,"uid":49784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T01:40:36.000Z","msg":"咩為個仔女好，去外國，唔想d 仔女香港學壞<br />\n<br />\n哂氣啦，又咪大話，外國都係d 自由社會<br />\n講民主果陣仲惡過香港<br />\n<br />\n真係想佢地好咩？<br />\n<br />\n好多都係利用d 仔女幫自己走咋<br />\nd 仔女坐定左係外國<br />\n可以申請埋自己走麻<br />\n<br />\n到時d 兄弟班，拍膊頭<br />\n果d 全部都係罪證，一話收番本passport <br />\n乜都講哂出黎啦<br />\n<br />\n所以話攪移民，仔女外國讀書果，全部都係鬼"},{"pid":"921864d4c8e74a4f7015fc9d40ee77f47e25a17c","tid":2008211,"uid":342828,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T01:55:31.000Z","msg":"所以狗隊高層呢個時候咪派埋D乜獎物獎嚟安撫吓D散仔囉。不過攞獎又點唧，都係condom嚟啫，唔通用完仲要戴住一世咩。"},{"pid":"55b0b64897ac9330603d06b70ba388a343f39c06","tid":2008211,"uid":49784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:24:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe75061bc5221ed38b21b1e81db2e7e6e471f00c","tid":2008211,"uid":53612,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:26:22.000Z","msg":"唔篤人就會比人篤<br />\n<br />\n呢樣真"},{"pid":"92574eded012134244b07984d06611ccd07ec79b","tid":2008211,"uid":49784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe75061bc5221ed38b21b1e81db2e7e6e471f00c","tid":2008211,"uid":53612,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:26:22.000Z","msg":"唔篤人就會比人篤<br />\n<br />\n呢樣真"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T06:09:29.000Z","msg":"只係鬥快，篤左未必即刻比人拉<br />\n<br />\n但係立法會選舉前，警察逐一被捕<br />\n今次只係前奏，試水溫<br />\n<br />\n因為選舉比警察重要<br />\n會用拘捕警察，換取民意<br />\n<br />\n再用&quot;傳媒&quot;標榜警察洗底，<br />\n令中間派選民認為香港政府都唔係太差<br />\n<br />\n只要警察職位唔夠大，即係大到陶輝咁<br />\n都可以送上法庭"},{"pid":"3d546fcf554f6bcdfb6ef5298f47e91fb4f8c1fe","tid":2008211,"uid":343080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T06:13:13.000Z","msg":"510 一齊出尖沙咀反對班狗嘅反對通知書！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2008512\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2008512</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"593cab1438a2146cebe381bba521938d0a2623e5","tid":2008211,"uid":49784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T06:14:55.000Z","msg":"立法會選舉比一切為大<br />\n<br />\n比警隊更重要，完成呢個立法會選舉<br />\n犧牲一部分警員嘅前途係在所難免<br />\n<br />\n只係睇下邊個比人篤先<br />\n<br />\n橫向平輩做過乜圍內實知<br />\n<br />\n仲有一樣，太多香港警察，對警隊黎講唔係好事<br />\n呢為亦係換血嘅好時機"},{"pid":"7afbf9935ec177f5d0d52d1010892b56eca96f07","tid":2008211,"uid":49784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T06:21:07.000Z","msg":"打人真係無證據？<br />\n<br />\n身邊個兄弟真係咁信得過？<br />\n<br />\n到佢地比人周果陣，唔通會守祕密咩<br />\n都係自私精<br />\n<br />\n將所有野推哂比d 兄弟<br />\n最多，咪幫手照顧下你老婆同個女"},{"pid":"9937e4cf1c8d3b813632264da17b01cf2dae8e27","tid":2008211,"uid":49784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T07:32:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60e3d4b45438d59e03319848d6cd39b3af3a454a","tid":2008211,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92574eded012134244b07984d06611ccd07ec79b","tid":2008211,"uid":49784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe75061bc5221ed38b21b1e81db2e7e6e471f00c","tid":2008211,"uid":53612,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:26:22.000Z","msg":"唔篤人就會比人篤<br />\n<br />\n呢樣真"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T06:09:29.000Z","msg":"只係鬥快，篤左未必即刻比人拉<br />\n<br />\n但係立法會選舉前，警察逐一被捕<br />\n今次只係前奏，試水溫<br />\n<br />\n因為選舉比警察重要<br />\n會用拘捕警察，換取民意<br />\n<br />\n再用&quot;傳媒&quot;標榜警察洗底，<br />\n令中間派選民認為香港政府都唔係太差<br />\n<br />\n只要警察職位唔夠大，即係大到陶輝咁<br />\n都可以送上法庭"},"citedBy":